doi:10.2307/2964111</li>

<li id="ref-Sch:1890">Schr&ouml;der, Ernst, 1890, <em>Vorlesungen
&uuml;ber die Algebra der Logik</em> (v. 1), Leipzig: Teubner.</li>

<li id="ref-scott1974completeness">Scott, Dana, 1974,
&ldquo;Completeness and Axiomatizability in Many-Valued Logic&rdquo;,
